headline: BP & CTVA Partner to Form Etlas JV for Biofuel Feedstock Supply
summary: BP teams up with Corteva to form Etlas, a 50-50 JV to grow oilseed crops for SAF and renewable diesel, targeting a large-scale low-carbon fuel supply.
